sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Cliente autenticado
    participant API as /auth/beaver-handoff
    participant DB as MySQL
    participant Bridge as hub_bridge
    participant Beaver as Beaver
    C->>API: Solicita handoff
    API->>DB: Valida usuario, tenant y membresía
    API->>Bridge: Genera JWT RS256 temporal
    Bridge-->>API: code, expires_in, beaver_tenant_id
    API-->>C: redirect_url, exchange_url, code
    C->>Beaver: Intercambia code en exchange_url
